The celebration continues as Spider-Man's 60th anniversary leads us to talk his THEATERICAL LEGACY. Join us as we go over every Spider-Man film that has been released in theaters and talk about what went right, wrong, and sideways when it comes to the Spidey franchise!   Please leave us a review on [ITunes](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us wherever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our [merchandise](http://www.teepublic.com/user/comicbookclique)! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by [ComicBookClique.com](episode/update/id/Comicbokclique.com), the home for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.

